### check if server is running
GET http://localhost:8080

### get all orders
GET http://localhost:8080/api/order

### get order 1
GET http://localhost:8080/api/order/1


### get invalid order 4711 -> should yield status 404
GET http://localhost:8080/api/order/4711

### create order
POST http://localhost:8080/api/order
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer": "Paula",
  "date": 1752135456157,
  "positions": []
}
### check new order ** copy new id into variable **
@orderID = 1752137056760
GET http://localhost:8080/api/order/{{orderID}}

### update order
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/order
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": {{orderID}},
  "customer": "Mohammed",
  "date": "1728556440000"
}

### verify update
GET http://localhost:8080/api/order/{{orderID}}

### delete new order 
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/order/{{orderID}}

